Package: mctaus
Title: Australian Multivariate Core Trend Inflation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Stephan", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bayesian mixed-frequency dynamic factor model for Australian
    CPI, producing a measure of trend inflation and a decomposition of
    where persistence is coming from (common vs sector-specific). An
    Australian analogue of the NY Fed's Multivariate Core Trend (MCT)
    inflation model. Estimation in Stan via cmdstanr; orchestration via
    targets; dashboard via Quarto.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
